  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Brexit guide: data protection for education providers
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Information for education providers on how to remain compliant with data protection laws when the UK leaves the EU.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

